definition: to count/to count as/to regard as/to enumerate (sb's shortcomings)

sentences.english: But a weed plant can produce tens or even hundreds of thousands of seeds.
sentences.chinese: 但每株杂草能产生数万甚至数十万颗种子。

sentences.english: It also caused tens of thousands of families to wait years before being reunited with their loved ones.
sentences.chinese: 这还导致数万个家庭在好些年都无法团聚。

sentences.english: Big corporate logos that need to represent a brand can cost tens of thousands of dollars.
sentences.chinese: 大公司往往耗资数万元来设计展现自己品牌的标志。

sentences.english: In Hama, videos show tens of thousands of people in the streets.
sentences.chinese: 在哈马，视频显示数万人在街道上抗议。

sentences.english: Tens of thousands of them, like Mrs. Young, were asked for specimens.
sentences.chinese: 他们中的数万人像杨女士一样被征集了唾液样本。

sentences.english: At present, the gourd sheets of different types of works created tens of thousands of pieces.
sentences.chinese: 目前，葫芦张已创作不同类型的作品数万幅。

sentences.english: They are making our thousands of warriors of the PLA go hungry in the cantonment .
sentences.chinese: 他们让数万人民解放军的战士们在营房里挨饿。

sentences.english: We trade about a trillion dollars in goods and services each year.
sentences.chinese: 欧美每年商品服务贸易额都达数万亿美元。

sentences.english: Mount Qiqu is world famous for its tens of thousands of ancient cypresses.
sentences.chinese: 七曲山以拥有数万株古柏而闻名于世。

sentences.english: Storage bins hold tons of wheat before being sold. (Todd Korol/Reuters)
sentences.chinese: 数万吨的小麦在被卖出之前被贮存在这些储藏箱里。

sentences.english: If our each person donates 20 yuan, we will donate tens of thousands at least.
sentences.chinese: 如果我们每个人捐赠20元，我们将至少捐赠数万。

sentences.english: Trillions of dollars have been spent "pump-priming" the US economy.
sentences.chinese: 数万亿的美元花在“刺激经济的政府投资”。

sentences.english: Hundreds of thousands of citizens are grieving over the death of this popular artist.
sentences.chinese: 数万市民来悼唁这位人民艺术家。

sentences.english: Tens of thousands were arrested on terrorism-related charges.
sentences.chinese: 数万人因被控告与恐怖主义有关而被捕。

sentences.english: You've still got trillions of pounds of debt around.
sentences.chinese: 你在各地仍然有数万亿英镑的欠债。

sentences.english: As long as gambling too long, losing thousands of dollars a night are not surprising.
sentences.chinese: 只要赌博时间过长，一晚上输掉数万元都不足为奇。
